# OpenFoundry — Code owners
#
# This file routes pull-request reviews to the team(s) responsible for each
# area of the monorepo. The last matching pattern wins, so put more specific
# rules below the generic ones.
#
# All entries below use placeholder GitHub team handles under the
# `@open-foundry` organisation. Replace them with the real team handles once
# the corresponding GitHub teams are created. Until then, GitHub will fall
# back to the `@open-foundry/maintainers` catch-all.
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default owners (catch-all)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
